According to the rules of Monster Fight, rematches come with

which is rooted in the lives of the citizens, be mismanaged
any longer...

Monster Fight does not prohibit losers from challenging
winners to reclaim what they bet. However, to prevent
battles from becoming quagmires, there are strict conditions
for requesting a rematch.

Memimi: (If the loser challenges the winner to a rematch,
they must obey one command from the winner, whatever it may
be... It's terrible, but either way, I'll just end up in a
similar situation if things stay as they are...!)

In Monster Fight, to achieve a rematch, the loser must carry
out any one command issued by the winner. To prevent their
winnings from being taken back, these commands are naturally
humiliating or dangerous.

Lackey: Boss, this chick's gone mad!! Nobody wants a

Haha...

Memimi: (Great leader... My fellow organization members,
